---
title: Goat Cheese-Stuffed Chicken Roulades with Kale & Couscous Salad
description: Tangy goat cheese and sweet sun-dried tomatoes make for a delicious, melty filling in this chicken roulade. If you've never "massaged" kale before, you're in for a surprise! It may sound strange, but a quick massage transforms raw kale into a tender, yet hearty green that's perfect for salads!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/552e797d6ced6e9a3c8b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/552e797d6ced6e9a3c8b4567.pdf
